article.description: — Landon Glasper's 19 points helped N.C. A&T defeat Campbell 76-62 on Thursday night.
article.headline: N.C. A&T takes down Campbell 76-62
article.story: GREENSBORO, N.C. -- — Landon Glasper's 19 points helped N.C. A&T defeat Campbell 76-62 on Thursday night. Glasper had seven rebounds for the Aggies (3-11, 1-0 Coastal Athletic Association). Camian Shell scored 18 points and added five assists. Jason Murphy shot 4 of 9 from the field and 2 for 3 from the free-throw line to finish with 10 points. Anthony Dell'Orso led the way for the Fighting Camels (6-8, 0-1) with 24 points and 10 rebounds. Laurynas Vaistaras added 13 points and three steals for Campbell. In addition, Jasin Sinani finished with 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
